OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, seriously injured
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder after a 13-year-old
OL,8,Fgirl was seriously injured in
OL,9,FNottinghamshire.
OL,11,FPolice said a 14-year-old boy, who
OL,12,Fcannot be named for legal reasons, was
OL,13,Farrested after an incident near
OL,14,FWensley Road in Woodthorpe in the
OL,15,FBorough of Gedling just before 4pm on
OL,16,FFriday 17th April.
OL,18,FHe is due to appear at Nottingham
OL,19,FYouth Court today charged with
OL,20,Fattempted murder and carrying a bladed
OL,21,Farticle.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
