OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, seriously injured
OL,6,FThe girl was taken to hospital and her
OL,7,Fcondition is described as stable.
OL,9,FSuperintendent James Woolley from
OL,10,FNottinghamshire Police said:
OL,12,F"Officers are supporting the victim
OL,13,Fand her family through this traumatic
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,F"We understand the impact an incident
OL,17,Flike this will have on the local
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOU
