OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, seriously injured
OL,6,F"I would like to reassure the public
OL,7,Fwe are doing everything we can to
OL,8,Funderstand the circumstances that has
OL,9,Fled to this attack.
OL,11,F"We have arrested and charged a 14-
OL,12,Fyear-old boy with attempted murder."
OL,14,FPolice are asking anyone with
OL,15,Finformation to call 101 quoting
OL,16,Fincident number 0532 of the April 17
OL,17,F2026 or call Crimestoppers anonymously
OL,18,Fon 0800 555 111.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@dO]
